item.title: NIKE Definition Bra - Spark Pink
item.description: Nike Definition Racerback Sports Bra: Sweat-wicking support. Sporting a sweat-wicking combo of breathability and snug support, the Nike Definition Racerback Women's Sports Bra is a hard-working, contoured essential that flatters while taking on medium-impact workouts. Benefitting from Dri-FIT fabric to wick sweat away and help keep you dry and comfortable, internal support frame for extra holding power, mesh racerback for ventilation and flat-seam construction to minimize chafing. Ideal for medium-impact sports like like cycling, dance and cardio classes. Fabric: 88% Polyester/12% Spandex

item.description: A Berlei best seller with maximum support and minimum bounce thanks to ultrasonic welding. Tried and tested by professional athletes, loved by runners everywhere! Breathable wire channelling wicks away sweat to keep you dry and double layered fabric for extra softness against the skin. Two ways to wear - fasten normally or cross-over straps. the flat wing design with no hard corners and no irritating labels.

Breathable wire channelling wicks away sweat to keep you dry and double layered fabric for extra softness against the skin. item.title: Merrell Bare Access Arc - Smoke
item.description: For distance runners and those new on the path to barefoot running, Merrell Bare Access Arc 0mm drop running shoe gives you a barefoot feel, with added toe to heel cushioning. Still allowing your foot to land flat and follow its own natural motion, its cushioning protects from sustained impacts due to longer runs or a new barefoot training program. UPPER / LINING: Barefoot strobel construction offers flexibility and comfort, synthetic leather and mesh upper, DWR-treated upper repels water and resists staining, reflective details for increased visibility in low light and Lycra neoprene lining for padded comfort treated with Aegis antimicrobial solution. MIDSOLE / OUTSOLE: 8mm M Bound allows for cushioned entry into Bareform movement, 0mm ball to heel drop keeps you connected to your terrain, wash as needed in cold water, gentle cycle and air dry, vegan friendly footwear, natural flex outsole with 2.5mm lug depth allows for dynamic foot movement and Merrell Bare Access Arc Sole / sticky rubber Pods. Womens Weight: 4.9 ozs (1/2 Pair)
item.g:google_product_category: Clothing & Accessories > Shoes > Athletics Shoes > Fitness & Cross Training Shoes

item.title: Saucony Progrid Stabil CS2 - White/Silver/Pink
item.description: RUN: Ultiimate Stability. Controlled Stability (CS) Zone provides ultimate stability, with flexibility for the severe overpronator. Stability Arch-Lock provides a supportive fit in the upper. UPPER: Stability Arch-Lock. Lightweight stretch materials in the arch area that extend to two eyelets and adapt to your foot to provide a snug and supportive midfoot fit. Hydrator Lining: Saucony's performance apparel fabric that provides next-to-skin comfort and maximizes wicking. Comfortride Sockliner: Saucony's exclusive open cell foam sockliner. It is antimicrobial and breathable while providing superior cushioning and ride. HRC Strobel Board: Increases cushioning and step-in comfort. MIDSOLE: Heel ProGrid with Respon-Tek Saucony's latest cushioning technology, ProGrid, absorbs impact, dissipates shock and sets the foot up for a smooth transition. Dual Density SSL (Saucony Super Lite) EVA. Saucony's most advanced EVA blend that maximizes rebound and durability while minimizing weight. CS Zone. Saucony's controlled stability zone provides maximum stability for overpronation while still maintaining optimal flexibility. SRC Impact Zone: Provides shock attenuation and sets the foot up for a smooth transition. SRC Forefoot Cushioning: Saucony's premier forefoot cushioning system provides a smooth toe-off. 12mm Offset: Heel-to-toe differential of the shoe, excluding the storbel board and sockliner. OUTSOLE: Blown Rubber. Lighweight flexibile material provides added cushioning while maintaining durability and a smooth ride. XT-900: A carbon rubber outsole material that offers exceptional traction properties without sacrificing durability.

Featuring Microwobbleboard technology. FitFlop footwear is built with patent-pending, biomechanically engineered Microwobbleboard midsoles. Originally designed to activate leg muscles more, studies show they also offer excellent shock absorption and instant relief from underfoot pressure. FitFlop footwear has the potential to increase muscle activity duration and workload, so should be used progressively. If you: a) have any health concerns, and/or b) are pregnant, and/or c) experience any discomfort as a result of wearing them, please consult a medical practitioner before starting or continuing to wear FitFlop footwear.

FitFlop footwear is built with patent-pending, biomechanically engineered Microwobbleboard midsoles. Originally designed to activate leg muscles more, studies show they also offer excellent shock absorption and instant relief from underfoot pressure. FitFlop footwear has the potential to increase muscle activity duration and workload, so should be used progressively. If you: a) have any health concerns, and/or b) are pregnant, and/or c) experience any discomfort as a result of wearing them, please consult a medical practitioner before starting or continuing to wear FitFlop footwear.
